        public abstract boolean inject(Pipeline pipeline,
                               BlockingQueue<Event> mainqueue,
                               boolean blocking)
        This method inject a new event in a pipeline as a top processing pipeline. Not to be used for sub-processing pipeline. It can only be used for a new event.
        Parameters:
        pipeline - the pipeline with the processes to inject
        mainqueue - the waiting queue
        blocking - does it block or fails if the queue is full.
        Returns:
        true if event was injected in the pipeline.
